  "texts": [
    "By using batch normalization, learning becomes more efficient.",
    "Moreover, to avoid over-fitting of a model it can be used as a regularization.",
    "To standardize the input or the outputs, the layer is added to the sequential model.",
    "It can be used at some several points in between layers of model.",
    "It is placed right after defining sequential model and after the convolution layers and pooling layers [82]."
